beer.beer_description: The big guns are out in this old school West Coast IPA with a fresh twist. A backbone made from Columbus, Centennial and Chinook provides the perfect platform for NZ's latest and greatest hop Nectaron. Intense tropical fruit and peach sit atop of piney resinous dankness. It's a cracker!
